data.description: Cuteness Overload! This updated Home is within a mile of downtown Monroe and all that the city has to offer. Originally built in 1930 but was rebuilt in 2022 with luxury vinyl flooring, gorgeous lighting, Stainless Steel appliances, Granite Kitchen with tile backsplash, and Fresh Interior Paint are just the beginning.  Huge front porch to enjoy for morning coffee or after a long day plus a side porch entrance to unload your groceries. Family room has a double-sided fireplace for a nice focal point and the high ceilings in this gem are awesome! The primary bedroom is so spacious and leads to your ensuite with beautiful finishes like dual vanity, tiled shower with glass doors, and a huge walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms and another updated bath with tub/shower & linen closet. The level lot extends long from the house with enough room for a firepit, playset, garden, and deck. Make this your new Home in Monroe for years to come!
